e ultimate\nperformance of FL, we propose both online and offline approaches to tackle the\nresulting design problem. Simulation results demonstrate that such a\nperformance-oriented design strategy can achieve higher test accuracy than the\nconventional isolated mean square error (MSE) minimization approach in FL.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Jun 2022 05:41:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 2 Nov 2022 02:40:20 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 26 Nov 2022 07:21:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-29"}
