he asteroid from ground telescopes.\nThe best opportunities will be during total solar eclipses.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Jun 2022 10:53:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 22 Nov 2022 13:34:10 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 24 Dec 2022 09:39:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-15"}
