ides a valuable tool to analyse extensive\nobservational datasets such as spectroscopic phase curves. Near-future\nobservations with missions such as the James Webb Space Telescope (JWST) and\nAriel will greatly improve our understanding of the atmospheres of exoplanets\nsuch as WASP-43b.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Jun 2022 12:29:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-31"}
