ompared to the initial iteration, i.e. the errors are significantly reduced.\nSubsequently, the remaining dependence structures of the residuals of the\nsecond smoother iteration can be captured by copula models. Their\ninterpretation is useful for a revision of the physical model utilized by the\nRTS smoother.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Jun 2022 14:40:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-22"}
